name: Cases with Rework (Any event repeated more than 3 times)
query:
SELECT case_id, "event_name", "end_time", "Risk Class" 
FROM "defaultview-9"
WHERE (SELECT MAX(occ)
       FROM (SELECT OCCURRENCE(event_name) AS occ) AS sub) > 3
ORDER BY 1
description: Rework means the same event_name occurrent multiple times in the same case
